Changed from version 0.41 --> 1.0

major changes: 

- NOTE: change of licence from GNU LGPL to GNU GPL (see COPYING)
- added version information 

minor changes: 
- changes of implementation of ghost information
- the load balance config file was renamed from `lastverteilung.cfg' to
  `loadbalancing.cfg' 
- twist lookup table also for hexa 

bug fixes: 

- restart from checkpoint works again 
- when coarsening ghost cell a never ending loop was removed 
- slight changes in the stream reading and writing procedure during load
  balancing which caused extreme long load balancing times on large
  meshes 


